            "Education"
        ],
        [
            "Almost each barrio or barangay in Piddig has its own elementary school.",
            "The town's poblacion Anao, historically had two, Piddig Central (North) and South Piddig Central elementary schools.",
            "Both schools are situated next to each other north of town.",
            "The schools' rivalry is legendary.",
            "In the late 1980s the schools merged as one, Piddig Central."
        ],
        [
            "There are three high schools in Piddig: Piddig National High School, Roosevelt High School, and St. Anne Academy (Catholic).",
            "However, many students attend high schools in nearby Laoag City."
        ],
